body:
This is only happening with Flutter projects, not Kotlin or Java projects. Somebody has reported it [here](https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/83777), with screenshots and other details. All I can do is append logs, though I dont't know how helpful they are.

This has been happening in both Android Studio 4.1 and 4.2 and I tested it on 2 different computers (one of them with a fresh new Windows 10 and Android Studio).

## Steps to Reproduce

Create a Flutter project in this environment

```

```
